MOTION DOCKET

96-1875. Consumers’ Counsel v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, Nos. 94-1964-EL-CSS, 95-1139-EL-COI, 95-1140-EL-COI, 95-299-*1459EL-AIR and 95-300-EL-AIR.

On motion for stay of Ohio Council of Retail Merchants. Motion granted.

Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., would grant a limited stay of only the Ohio Council of Retail Merchants’ portion. Resnick, J., not participating.
